  <summary date="2021-07-08T22:09:22Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Medical Nutrition Equity Act of 2021

This bill expands coverage under Medicare, Medicaid, other specified federal health care programs, and private health insurance&#160;to include foods, vitamins, and individual amino acids that are medically necessary for the management of&#160;certain digestive and metabolic disorders&#160;and conditions.</summary>
